WEBVTT

00:02.010 --> 00:06.040 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
It’s a really Aussie thing, that parents have done all the time

00:06.170 --> 00:09.130 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
is put the sprinkler on for the kids in the heat in summer. 

00:09.220 --> 00:12.150 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
That’s what Australian poor families have always done.

00:12.160 --> 00:16.000 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
Like I grew up playing in the sprinkler in summer to beat the heat.

00:16.020 --> 00:22.190 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
We can’t do that. None of the towns can do that because everyone’s on water restrictions and we’re not supposed to have the sprinklers running.

00:22.240 --> 00:25.220 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
The whole time that we’ve been fighting for water here in our village,

00:26.030 --> 00:28.000 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
it’s only been for basic use.

00:28.130 --> 00:33.080 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
We’re only allowed to use our allocated water for drinking,

00:33.120 --> 00:36.220 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
flushing the toilet, washing, cooking.

00:37.070 --> 00:38.140 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
Just general household use. 

00:39.010 --> 00:41.190 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
And we had to fight really, really, really hard

00:41.200 --> 00:44.100 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
to even get that basic water allowance.

00:45.090 --> 00:48.080 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
That really concerned me why that would be the case,

00:48.090 --> 00:49.110 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
in a first world country. 

00:53.150 --> 00:57.090 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
My little son who’s seven, he said to me the other day,

00:57.180 --> 01:01.090 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
“Mum, when I grow up I’d love to buy some land and grow bush tucker

01:01.220 --> 01:03.090 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
… if we survive.”

01:03.140 --> 01:05.130 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
I said, “What do you mean, ‘if we survive’?”.

01:05.200 --> 01:09.010 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
He said, “Well, if we survive climate change.”

01:09.170 --> 01:13.130 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
And I was in a lot of shock over his comment.

01:14.140 --> 01:17.200 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
 Even though he’s only seven

01:18.100 --> 01:21.080 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
he’s aware that it’s a survival issue at the moment,

01:21.200 --> 01:27.120 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
 that climate change is so worrying to him as a seven-year-old.

01:29.210 --> 01:33.240 size:80% 
<v Fleur Magick Dennis><b>Fleur Magick Dennis</b>
That’s he’s just so worried about his future.



